def main():
    x = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
    if x[0] < x[1]:
        print('<')
    elif x[0] == x[1]:
        print('=')
    else:
        print('>')

elif a * b == c:
    print(str(a) + '*' + str(b) + '=' + str(c))
elif a / b == c:
    print(str(a) + '/' + str(b) + '=' + str(c))
elif a == b + c:
    print(str(a) + '=' + str(b) + '+' + str(c))
elif a == b - c:
    print(str(a) + '=' + str(b) + '-' + str(c))
elif a == b * c:
    print(str(a) + '=' + str(b) + '*' + str(c))
elif a == b / c:
    print(str(a) + '=' + str(b) + '/' + str(c))
